    "text": "The 10 m LSOG product is resampled to the exact spatial resolution and grid alignment of the Hagan et al. LiDAR map.",
    "topic": "Spatial harmonization"
  },
  {
    "text": "A documented crosswalk maps LSOG classes to the same legend as the LiDAR classification.",
    "topic": "Thematic consistency"
  },
  {
    "text": "The comparison is restricted to pixels where both maps have cloud-free and valid data.",
    "topic": "Valid data mask"
  },
  {
    "text": "Design-based population estimates from the LSOG product are converted to map-based area estimates prior to comparison with the LiDAR map.",
    "topic": "Estimation framework alignment"
  }
]
